  {
    "title": "Heavenly Artifacts - Solar Spear",
    "depth": 1,
    "paragraphs": [
      {
        "sentences": [
          {
            "text": "Gods fell and many a Heavenly Artifact was destroyed in the Great War of Gods.",
            "formatting": {
              "bold": [
                "Heavenly Artifact"
              ]
            }
          },
          {
            "text": "Only a few of such artifacts are left intact and scattered around the world, quietly waiting to be discovered after millennia of slumber."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "sentences": [
          {
            "text": "Some are all-conquering weapons, while some are items with special abilities."
          },
          {
            "text": "But one thing is for certain: All of these artifacts possess mysterious power to change the fate of a mortal, and one may even conquer the world with just one of them."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "sentences": [
          {
            "text": "As the head disciple of the Ziyang Sect, is naturally talented and has been in the Sect since childhood."
          },
          {
            "text": "At the age of 16, he felt a force reaching out to him when training alone, and found a spear beneath the stones in the creek on the back hills of the Sect."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "sentences": [
          {
            "text": "The spear was once again exposed to the world, as a dragon spirit flew out of it and into, choosing him as its master."
          },
          {
            "text": "The Dragon Soul is the inner spirit of the Solar Spear and may enter the Spear and fight enemies with at his command."
          }
        ]
      }
    ],
